entries.meaning: (rare) comparative form of gas: more gas
examples: This picture makes me miss seeing my friends every single day and thinking were [sic] gasser than we are ️♥ ♥ muchos lovos galpals

entries.meaning: One who gasses, or poisons with gas.
examples: Poison-gas fortunately proved to be a two-edged weapon when it was used on the battlefield.  […]  The wind could turn about to gas the gassers.

definitionGroups.group: A kind of hot rod based on production models from the 1930s to mid-1960s, stripped of extraneous weight and jacked up using a truck beam axle to provide better weight distribution on acceleration.

entries.meaning: More generally, any car or truck that runs on pump gas, as opposed to diesel fuel, racing fuel, or a car with an electric motor.
